-1.title: Win or Die
-1.plot: Whether it's getting the most food, the best territory, or the chance to mate, all animals compete against each other to survive. We examine some of the most intense power struggles in the animal kingdom. A group of bachelor baboons conspire to overthrow an alpha male, but it doesn't quite turn out as planned. An alpha female meerkat ousts her daughter from the clan when she becomes a threat, and worker bumblebees attack their queen.

imdb.title: Deadly Instincts
plot: The rules are different in the wild, it's kill or be killed. Learn how animals kill.::Geno LSP
